OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFuture of Scottish ice     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frinks at 'critical stage'  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Many of Scotland's ice rinks face      
OL,6, closure due to crippling energy bills, 
OL,7, a leading industry figure has warned.  
OL,9,FAyr Ice Rink confirmed it would shut   
OL,10,Fits doors permanently in September     
OL,11,Fsolely due to unprecedented hikes in   
OL,12,Fthe cost of gas and electricity.       
OL,14,FScottish Ice Rink Association president
OL,15,FMike Ferguson said his Forfar          
OL,16,Fbusiness's monthly gas bill is set to  
OL,17,Frise from #2,000 to #14,500.           
OL,19,FHe said several Scottish ice rinks were
OL,20,Fnow at "the critical stage."           
